          "reviewBody": "One of the best schools in Bhopal for all round development of children, dedication of the teachers and staff is commendable.Infrastructure wise also properly lit and airy classrooms, sports rooms\nSkill Enrichment and tasty ,healthy ,hygenic satvik food are there USPs\nChildren never want to miss a single day to school",
