        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Sagar Public School - Bhopal"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Sanchi Chaturvadi"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-03-29",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Dear Sagar Public School Administration,\nAs a parent, I am grateful for the efforts made by the school to provide a supportive learning environment, especially during these challenging times. The dedication of the teachers and staff in ensuring continuity of classes and providing resources for remote learning, and maintaining communication with parents/students has not gone unnoticed.\n\nI would like to take this opportunity to commend the school for its proactive approach in addressing the needs of students and fostering a sense of community, even in a virtual setting. Your commitment to academic excellence and the holistic development of students is truly commendable.\n\nThank you for your unwavering dedication and hard work. I am confident that with the continued support of the Sagar Public School community, we will overcome any challenges and continue to thrive.\n\nWarm regards,\n\nSanchi Tiwari\nMother of Nyesha Tiwari",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
