            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My experience with the school policy discussion was extremely disappointing. The policymakers have established a one-way communication system where parents are not allowed to question or provide input. This approach is particularly frustrating for parents who sacrifice so much to educate their children. I cannot recommend this school to anyone, especially to parents who prioritize their children's education and want to be actively involved",
